Program: Discovery
Title: Life in a box versus life in space
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwnc
Last Broadcast Date: 22 April 1996
Can life be made to survive in a box, the programme looks at the Ecotron project. Life in a box and life in space, how the first can help us with the latter. Also in the programme a new approach to tuberculosis and, do you need to be mad to be a scientist?